OL,3,GUK weather for today and tomorrow
OL,4,
OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FEvening rain
OL,6,Facross Scotland, becoming confined to
OL,7,FShetland. Otherwise, a dry evening and
OL,8,Fnight, with clear spells. Some fog
OL,9,Fdeveloping during the early hours in
OL,10,Fthe southwest. Rain arriving into the
OL,11,Ffar northwest towards dawn. Staying
OL,12,Fwarm in the southeast.
OL,13,
OL,14,CSaturday:FRain, heavy at times, will
OL,15,Fmove eastwards across Scotland and
OL,16,FNorthern Ireland, moving across
OL,17,FEngland and Wales during the evening
OL,18,Fand overnight. Ahead of this, plenty
OL,19,Fof warm sunny spells.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
